entries.s_fbe44b83: Jedi! I want nothing to do with anything Jedi.
entries.s_f5349262: Ye be wise beyond ye years for making that decision. I be wrong in thinking that ye could hold ye own with the likes of Jedi.
entries.s_f2e88b32: Jedi eh? And I suppose you will pay for these artifacts?
entries.s_ba5cc7c: Excellent. Let me look at what ye got for me. How nice...how nice indeed. I will make an offer on these. Ye should take me up on my offer because no one else will pay for what ye got.
entries.s_953d967f: Ummm...I think you have me confused for someone else.
entries.s_87c4b1c3: Lookie lookie what I see here. Ye certainly be a brave sort. The type that be trying to make a name for ye. Perhaps I be able to help ye make that name?
entries.s_86df00aa: I have ye curious now. I be looking for rare artifacts of the mysterious nature. Artifacts that this planet have in abundance. Artifacts of jedi.
entries.s_6e11f342: I don't have anything you would be interested in.
entries.s_5bc0c939: Pay and pay well. I be working for a collector who has credits to spend. Ye get me artifacts and I get ye credits.
entries.s_463bc6c4: I just might have some things you would be interested in.
entries.s_413bfd08: Well if ye find any Jedi artifacts ye know where I be.
entries.s_35b56f0a: Oh, well have I now. In that case ye should go about ye business.
